  <li id="comment-18833" class="comment even thread-even depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Amy</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2009/12/for-ever-and-ever/#comment-18833"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2009-12-15T07:15:15-05:00">Tuesday, December 15, 2009 at 7:15 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I just finished making a batch, and I don&#39;t think it&#39;s going to make it off the cookie sheet. Amazing!</p>
<p>One thing: I started the caramel as the popcorn was popping &#8212; and burned the popcorn. So I had to start a new bag, and rushed to get the caramel on the popcorn &#8230; and forgot to pick out the unpopped kernels. Microwave popcorn has a LOT of unpopped kernels. So, people, be sure you have your popcorn popped and de-kerneled beforehand.</p>
    </div>

