      <p>This caramel corn is the best! from flavor to texture I just love it. I saw similar recipe on smitten kitchen but it was &#39;adult&#39; spicy caramel corn&#8230;&#8230;so I upped the salt in this recipe to 1 tsp sea salt and added 1/4 tsp cayenne pepper and ooh ooh ooh not overly spicy but with just enough warmth&#8230;mmm mmm good</p>
    </div>

