    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I agree, all I ever want to do is eat this popcorn.  I&#39;m going about my day and I get a craving to eat caramel corn. Thanks for this recipe! My sister and I have made it many times. It&#39;s so easy and so delicious!</p>
    </div>

